data.description: Welcome to this beautiful home offering the perfect blend of convenience and tranquility! As you enter, be greeted by the warmth of new wood floors that adorn the entryway and extend into the living room which boasts a stunning fireplace and vaulted ceilings. Adjacent to the living room, the well-appointed kitchen beckons with its abundance of granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, and an expansive island with cooktop. A formal dining room nearby sets the stage for intimate dinners or gatherings. The convenience continues with a utility room equipped with built-in cabinets and a dog wash station. Retreat to the luxurious primary bedroom offering an ensuite bath complete with a breathtaking standing shower and 2 large walk-in closets. 2 additional bedrooms provide ample space for all. Outside, discover a fully fenced backyard oasis featuring a large covered patio, perfect for al fresco dining, and a stone hot tub, promising endless relaxation and enjoyment under the open sky.
